Package: clparlysearch
Type: Package
Title: Download data on Members' activities in Parliament from parliamentary search
Version: 0.1.2
Author: Elise Uberoi
Maintainer: Elise Uberoi <eliseuberoi@gmail.com>
Description: This package enables users to get data on Members' activities in Parliament:
    their contributions to debates, the questions they ask and the Early Day Motions they
    sign. The package gives a row for each activity for each MP in a defined period. 
    Data is retrieved from Parliamentary Search.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
